item.title: Logo Animation Music
Synth Experiments
item.description: In college I messed around quite a bit with Reason. I used it to create the soundtrack for Pact Lunch and a bunch of other little clips for various video projects. Most of those ideas came out of a creative challenge I gave myself. I had to wait until I was just about to fall asleep, and then fire up Reason and record any idea until I collapsed at my desk.
